name: NYDailyNews
text:
RT @NYDailyNews: “This is not right.”

With less than 48 hours' notice, NYC began moving disabled people out of a Midtown shelter to make room for homeless people an Upper West Side community wanted out, the Daily News learned.

“They’re treating us like we’re toys.”
